title: Ultimo Designs Heavy-Duty Oversized Storage Bags with Zip & Clear Tag Pocket – Water-Resistant, Durable Organizer for Moving, Clothes, Laundry, Packing & Home Storage (Clear, 4 Pack)
features: Flexible & Sustainable Storage Solution - Declutter and organize effortlessly with Ultimo Designs’ extra-large storage bag crafted to be more versatile, stylish, and convenient than traditional storage bins. Perfect for storing seasonal clothing, bedding, cushions, and more, these flexible bags maximize space while allowing for easy stacking and storage. Dimensions: 70W x 42H x 35D cm, Capacity: 102 Liters

Move Without Boxes, Ditch the hassle of bulky boxes and packing tape! Ultimo Designs’ large and durable moving bags offer a lightweight, convenient, and cost-effective alternative to traditional moving boxes and bins. Simply unfold, unzip, and start packing—perfect for transporting household essentials. Designed for versatility, these spacious bags also double as clothing storage, under-bed organizers, laundry bags, or seasonal storage for bedding, blankets, or even your Christmas tree.

Effortless Organization with a Clear Design & Tag Pocket - Say goodbye to endless searching! Ultimo Designs’ storage bags feature a clear tag pocket, allowing you to quickly identify your belongings at a glance. Simply insert a custom label for easy recognition and hassle-free organization, perfect for streamlining storage in your home, office, or move. Stay organized, save time, and enjoy effortless convenience with Ultimo Designs.

Heavy-Duty & Water-Resistant for Reliable Storage - Ultimo Designs’ storage bags are built to handle heavy loads up to 27 kg, featuring two sets of reinforced poly webbing handles—top carrying handles for easy lifting and sturdy side handles for convenient transport. Crafted from durable, water-resistant fabric, these bags are made to last while keeping your belongings protected. Simply wipe the interior and exterior with a damp cloth or sanitizing wipe, then air dry for long-lasting use.

Wide opening Design, Pack with Ease. No more struggling to fit your items. Ultimo Designs’ storage bag opens wide like a suitcase, making packing and unpacking effortless. Easily place and remove your belongings without hassle—perfect for moving, organizing, or travel. When not in use, simply collapse and fold flat for compact storage in your drawer, cabinet, closet, garage, luggage, or car boot. Opt for a stylish & reusable storage solution with Ultimo Designs.
